  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><center><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/05/windows-rt-to-come-with-outlook-app-starting-with-windows-8-1/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/msdsc03774-13704116281.jpg\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; margin: 4px;\" /></a></center>\n<br />\n<br />\n微软本月底即将举行开发者大会，所以早预期这次 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/Computex/\">Computex</a> 不会有太多惊喜。但今天确实放出一些消息，例如 x86 计算机会附送 office 应用。而 Windows RT 平板计算机也被确认将随 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/Windows81/\">Windows 8.1</a> 更新，预载 Outlook 软件。众所皆知这次重大更新将在 6 月 26 日开始发送预览版本。<br />\n<br />\n此外官方 blog 还提到在接下来一个星期左右，将提供针对 Touch Cover 和 Type Cover 两项键盘配件的操作更新。例如亮度调整、页面卷动、常用功能键及音量调整等组合键操作（Fn+特定按键）。到目前为止，微软尚未对于 RT 系统的总体更新幅度做更详细的说明，相信在接下来几周会逐渐明朗。<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/06/05/windows-rt-to-come-with-outlook-app-starting-with-windows-8-1/\">Engadget</a><br />\n数据源：<a href=\"http://blogs.office.com/b/office-news/archive/2013/06/05/outlook-2013-rt-coming-to-windows-rt-tablets-as-part-of-windows-8-1-update.aspx\">Office Blog</a>, <a href=\"http://blog.surface.com/b/surface/archive/2013/06/05/outlook-2013-rt-coming-to-surface-rt-and-more.aspx\">Surface Blog</a><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/05/windows-rt-to-come-with-outlook-app-starting-with-windows-8-1/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20601129/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/05/windows-rt-to-come-with-outlook-app-starting-with-windows-8-1/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
